text: Münsterländer may refer to: *A person from the German region of Münster *One of two breeds of dogs of the gun dog type originating in the Münster region of Germany: **Large Münsterländer, a breed of dog weighing approximately 30 kg (66 lbs) **Small Münsterländer, a breed of dog weighing approximately 16 kg (35 lbs) Category:Münster (region)
title: Münsterländer
